                            <comment id="233020" author="jhammond" created="Wed, 5 Sep 2018 01:58:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just to repeat my comment, I think this is due to a llog issue. (Which may be exposed in some ray by recent changes.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I looked at this a bit. When it works the params log is processed normally. When it doesn&apos;t work mgc_process_log() skips the params log since cld-&amp;gt;cld_stopping is set. So I think this is due finding an old CLD of the params log.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
