&lt;p&gt;If you run:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;udevadm monitor --subsystem-match=lustre --property&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You should see the uevents being sent and what values.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
